True that is, but ill tell you why: 
This is _not_ a film review site, nor is it "the movie club" where we discuss what movies we like or not, we dont discuss whats crap or good with the movies, what should be changed or is the best part of a movie.. 
Here we dl the movies we like, and all like different movies. Some love certain movies and some hate the same ones. We are only interested in what quality the ripped movie file has.. and we help each other with certain problems, warn about viruses, if it works with ps3, fakes and so on. And ofc throw crap at each other from time to time :)
For film criticism/rewiev/rating of movies i would suggest u go to another site/forum.
